<h1><a href="http://rubyforge.org/projects/rightscale">RightScale Gems</a></h1>

<p> RightScale's open-source gems provide Ruby-language interfaces to several
cloud computing platforms.  All the gems are freely available under the MIT
license.  For support, see the <a href="http://forums.rightscale.com">RightScale
	forums</a>.  The public Git repositories for all gems will be available
soon. 

<p>Thanks for using the Gems!

<p>- The RightScale team (rubygems [at] rightscale.com)

<p><h2><a href="http://rubyforge.org/projects/rightscale">RightAws (right_aws)</a></h2>

The <a href="http://rightscale.rubyforge.org/right_aws_gem_doc">RightAws RDoc</a> contains interface
documentation and usage information for the current release.

<p><h2><a href="http://rubyforge.org/projects/rightscale">RightGoGrid (right_gogrid)</a></h2>

<p>This gem is a Ruby-language interface to GoGrid's API.  The <a href="http://rightscale.rubyforge.org/right_gogrid_gem_doc">RightGoGrid RDoc</a> contains interface
documentation and usage information for the current release.
GoGrid publishes useful <a
	href="http://www.gogrid.com/how-it-works/gogrid-API.php">information on
	the API</a>.

<p><h2><a href="http://rubyforge.org/projects/rightscale">RightSlicehost (right_slicehost)</a></h2>

<p> The <a href="http:/www.slicehost.com">Slicehost site</a> explains the basic platform. The <a href="http://rightscale.rubyforge.org/right_slicehost_gem_doc">RightSlicehost RDoc</a> contains interface
documentation and usage information for the current release of the gem.

<p><h2><a href="http://rubyforge.org/projects/rightscale">RightFlexiscale (right_flexiscale)</a></h2>

<p> Some information on the Flexiscale platform is available at <a href="http://www.flexiscale.com">www.flexiscale.com</a>. The <a href="http://rightscale.rubyforge.org/right_flexiscale_gem_doc">RightFlexiscale RDoc</a> contains interface
documentation and usage information for the current release.

<p><h2><a href="http://rubyforge.org/projects/rightscale">RightHttpConnection (right_http_connection)</a></h2>

<p>
The <a href="http://rightscale.rubyforge.org/right_http_gem_doc">RightHttpConnection RDoc</a> contains interface
documentation and usage information for the current release.

